data.description: NEW CONSTRUCTION BY PREMIER BUILDER STELLA ROSE HOMES.  Positioned on a quiet cul-de-sac, this striking home has an open concept floor plan, vaulted ceilings, custom cabinets, granite, stainless steel appliance package, & modern electric fireplace. Practical kitchen design with sizable island offers functional flow for daily use & when entertaining guests. Generous master bedroom & elegant master bath offers dual sinks, grand walk-in shower with dual shower heads & stylish finishes. Energy efficient spray foam insulation & radiant barrier for more economical heating & cooling bills. 2-10 Warranty included. $2,000 buyer incentive - ask for details. Estimated Completion late January to early Feb 2020.
